sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/CI
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Webhook as kserve-webhook-server<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+ mTLS
    participant Controller as kserve-controller-manager<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    participant KnativeAPI as Knative API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant IstioAPI as Istio API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as Istio Ingress Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Activator as Knative Activator<br/>8012/TCP mTLS
    participant StorageInit as storage-initializer<br/>Init Container
    participant S3 as S3/GCS Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Predictor as Predictor Pod<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant Agent as kserve-agent<br/>Sidecar (localhost)
    participant ModelServer as Model Server<br/>8080/TCP (localhost)

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over User,IstioAPI: Flow 1: InferenceService Creation and Deployment
        User->>K8sAPI: Create InferenceService<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (kubeconfig)
        K8sAPI->>Webhook: Admission Request<br/>POST /mutate-serving-kserve-io-v1beta1-inferenceservice<br/>mTLS (CA bundle)
        Webhook->>K8sAPI: Mutated InferenceService<br/>Response
        K8sAPI->>Webhook: Validation Request<br/>POST /validate-serving-kserve-io-v1beta1-inferenceservice
        Webhook->>K8sAPI: Validation Result
        K8sAPI->>Controller: InferenceService Created<br/>Watch Event
        Controller->>KnativeAPI: Create Knative Service<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
        Controller->>IstioAPI: Create VirtualService<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    end

    rect rgb(255, 250, 240)
        Note over Client,ModelServer: Flow 2: Model Inference Request (Serverless Mode)
        Client->>Gateway: POST /v2/models/model:infer<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS1.2+<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (optional)
        Gateway->>Activator: Forward Request<br/>HTTP/8012 mTLS (Istio)
        Note over Activator: Scale from zero if needed
        Activator->>Predictor: Inference Request<br/>HTTP/8080 mTLS (Istio)

        Note over StorageInit,S3: Init Container Model Download (one-time)
        StorageInit->>S3: Download Model Artifacts<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS1.2+<br/>Auth: AWS IAM/GCS SA
        S3-->>StorageInit: Model Files
        Note over StorageInit,Predictor: Mount model volume

        Predictor->>Agent: Forward Request<br/>HTTP localhost (no encryption)
        Agent->>ModelServer: Inference Request<br/>HTTP localhost
        ModelServer-->>Agent: Prediction Result
        Agent-->>Predictor: Response
        Predictor-->>Activator: Response
        Activator-->>Gateway: Response
        Gateway-->>Client: JSON Response<br/>HTTPS/443
    end

    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
        Note over Client,Controller: Flow 3: InferenceGraph Multi-Model Pipeline
        participant Router as kserve-router<br/>8080/TCP HTTP mTLS
        participant Preprocess as Preprocessing IS<br/>80/TCP HTTP mTLS
        participant MainModel as Main Model IS<br/>80/TCP HTTP mTLS
        participant Postprocess as Postprocessing IS<br/>80/TCP HTTP mTLS

        Client->>Gateway: POST /v2/models/pipeline:infer<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS1.2+
        Gateway->>Router: Forward Request<br/>HTTP/8080 mTLS (Istio)
        Router->>Preprocess: Step 1: Preprocess<br/>HTTP/80 mTLS (Istio)
        Preprocess-->>Router: Preprocessed Data
        Router->>MainModel: Step 2: Inference<br/>HTTP/80 mTLS (Istio)
        MainModel-->>Router: Model Prediction
        Router->>Postprocess: Step 3: Postprocess<br/>HTTP/80 mTLS (Istio)
        Postprocess-->>Router: Final Result
        Router-->>Gateway: Response
        Gateway-->>Client: JSON Response
    end

    rect rgb(255, 240, 245)
        Note over User,Predictor: Flow 4: Model Update with Canary Rollout
        participant PredictorV1 as Predictor v1<br/>90% traffic
        participant PredictorV2 as Predictor v2<br/>10% traffic

        User->>K8sAPI: Update InferenceService<br/>New model version<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        K8sAPI->>Controller: Update Event
        Controller->>KnativeAPI: Create New Revision<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
        Controller->>IstioAPI: Update VirtualService<br/>Traffic Split: 90/10<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
        Client->>Gateway: Inference Request
        alt 90% traffic
            Gateway->>PredictorV1: Route to v1<br/>mTLS
            PredictorV1-->>Gateway: Response
        else 10% traffic
            Gateway->>PredictorV2: Route to v2<br/>mTLS
            PredictorV2-->>Gateway: Response
        end
        Gateway-->>Client: Response
    end
